snippet.title: Starship Troopers: Terran Command - Urban Onslaught | Teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Big announcement for Troopers!
Get ready to play a new DLC in Starship Troopers: Terran Command. Urban Onslaught is coming in June 2024.

🎮 Wishlist it on Steam ➡️ http://steam.gs/l/kpa12
💬 Join the Discord Server ➡️ https://discord.com/invite/xcASw4FQYn
